The paper focuses on using Wikipedia for natural language processing, information retrieval, information extraction, and ontology building. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the categories of computational linguistics (cs.CL), information retrieval (cs.IR), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and databases (cs.DB).
